{"tid":2164379,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"籲百佳惠康全數補貼回饋市民 邵家輝：李嘉誠唔會貪你嗰億幾","createTime":"2020-08-19T07:22:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T07:25:52.000Z","uid":241764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"354c4419ecce54f02a1bb2bc5d1aab313a086487","tid":2164379,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T07:22:49.000Z","msg":"政府昨宣佈月底開始申請第二期保就業計劃，並要求兩大超市百佳及惠康要領取補貼後，為顧客提供減價優惠。批發及零售界立法會議員邵家輝今早在港台節目中，認為派發現金券較為「真金白銀」，市民「條氣會順一點」，又指長和系資深顧問李嘉誠早前曾向業界捐贈約20億元，正常不會「貪你個億幾（補助）」，不介意要政府要求下全數補貼回饋市民。<br />\n<br />\n全文: <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200819/2P2FN5GTPJGBFKTGYELRX3O5HE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0YzEflAhSxZYcmK_HTjBwA4vcFIGlIq5soxFqfVHLYWcTATfoLn0lvRP8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200819%2F2P2FN5GTPJGBFKTGYELRX3O5HE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0YzEflAhSxZYcmK_HTjBwA4vcFIGlIq5soxFqfVHLYWcTATfoLn0lvRP8&d=MYvC0VRZm9a3oqKPvUvInGLrBTEyyW%2B%2F%2BTJtsqEcrWg%3D&h=80ec2375\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200819%2F2P2FN5GTPJGBFKTGYELRX3O5HE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0YzEflAhSxZYcmK_HTjBwA4vcFIGlIq5soxFqfVHLYWcTATfoLn0lvRP8&h=2fcb3678\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200819/2P2FN5GTPJGBFKTGYELRX3O5HE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0YzEflAhSxZYcmK_HTjBwA4vcFIGlIq5soxFqfVHLYWcTATfoLn0lvRP8</a>"},{"pid":"f405f1837b00c972c18caa1cab48d1b96f3ab564","tid":2164379,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T07:24:52.000Z","msg":"柒婆(國際公認反人類罪犯) 好心就回水"},{"pid":